    <item>
      <title>力拓将巨型几内亚铁矿成本定为 62 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/rio-to-spend-6-2-billion-to-develop-vast-africa-iron-ore-mine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[力拓集团将斥资约62亿美元开发几内亚巨大的西芒杜铁矿，这是其对马拉松项目的第一个官方估计，该项目旨在为寻求控制排放的钢铁制造商提供高质量的材料。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/rio-to-spend-6-2-billion-to-develop-vast-africa-iron-ore-mine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 21:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
